high_descs: Step forward, then turn left and move forward to go around the counter, then turn left and go straight toward the stove, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the large spoon from the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Clean the large spoon in the sink.
Go right, to go to the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Place the large spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large spoon on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left to the stove and face the counter to the left.
Pick up the spoon with the blue handle from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the spoon inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk to the counter on the left with the coffee maker.
Put the spoon on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spoon on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward just past the counter on the left, then turn left and walk to the counter by the stove top, finally turn left towards the ladle on the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn right, walk slightly forward, then turn left towards the coffee machine.
Put the ladle on the counter, in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned ladle on a counter top.
